resources.string: Weekly payments, auto renew, cancel anytime.

Payment will be charged to your Google Play account upon confirmation of purchase
 Subscription will automatically renew according to the subscription plan you choose unless canceled 24 hours before the end of the current subscription plan
 Non-subscribed users can still use the application however some paid features may be limited
 You can manage your subscription or cancel your subscription at any time in
